snippet.title: Pokémon TCG Pocket: Triumphant Light | Coming February 28!
snippet.description:
Happy Pokémon Day! Pokémon TCG Pocket is celebrating by releasing its fourth expansion, Triumphant Light, on February 28! The Mythical Pokémon Arceus will descend from the Sinnoh region as a powerful Pokémon ex, headlining an expansion that includes mighty Pokémon ex cards, new Trainer cards, gorgeous immersive cards, and the unveiling of Pokémon with unique Link Abilities. Look forward to free booster packs with rare cards at a special Pokémon Day in-game event celebrating the release of Triumphant Light.

Official site: https://www.pokemon.com
